Host: localhost
Port: 11000
Transmission Encoding: TCP
Data Encoding: Text

Register function:
Request: REGISTER%%$username%%$password
Response: ADDED
or
Response: USERNAME_TAKEN
or
Response: INVALID_PASSWORD
or
Response: INVALID_USERNAME

Login function:
Request: LOGIN%%$username%%$password
Response: SUCCESSFUL
or
Response: FAILED
or
Response: INVALID_REQUEST
or
Response: USER_NOT_FOUND


Send Email function:
Request: SEND%%$recipient%%$subject%%$content
Response: EMAIL_SENT
or
Response: USER_NOT_FOUND
or
Response: INVALID_EMAIL_FORMAT


List Received Emails:
Request: LIST_RECEIVED
Response: EMAIL%%$id%%$sender%%$subject%%$timestamp

or
Response: NO_EMAILS_FOUND

Read Email:
Request: READ%%$id
Response: EMAIL_CONTENT%%$content
or
Response: EMAIL_NOT_FOUND


Logout function:
Request: LOGOUT
Response: LOGGED_OUT
or
Response: INVALID_REQUEST